Description: 
    Creates a side-by-side boxplot for a continuous variable 
    grouped by a two-level categorical variable, checks normality 
    assumptions, and runs the appropriate statistical test 
    (t-test or Wilcoxon rank-sum test). Returns a publication-ready plot 
    and test statistics including test statistic, degrees of freedom, 
    and p-value.
